name: r-diffr
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.1' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-diffr
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/diffr_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/diffr/diffr_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: e82ec76b4eadee8ec682f83a8a9d3ffe6309fc31e6c66db573d6e7f8fdb5bc79

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1004
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-htmlwidgets
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-htmlwidgets

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('diffr')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('diffr')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=diffr
  license: GPL-2.0-only
  summary: An R interface to the 'codediff' JavaScript library (a copy of which is included in
    the package, see <https://github.com/danvk/codediff.js> for information). Allows
    for visualization of the difference between 2 files, usually text files or R scripts,
    in a browser.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - FrodePedersen
    - ArneKr
    - MathiasHaudgaard

# Package: diffr
# Title: Display Differences Between Two Files using Codediff Library
# Version: 0.1
# Authors@R: person("John", "Muschelli", email = "muschellij2@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
# Description: An R interface to the 'codediff' JavaScript library (a copy of which is included in the package, see <https://github.com/danvk/codediff.js> for information). Allows for visualization of the difference between 2 files, usually text files or R scripts, in a browser.
# Depends: R (>= 3.0)
